title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 4 categories of Response on the x axis representing 2 groups: Remain, and Leave.

Followed by Lower Middle-Class (C1) with a mean value of 50.0.
The lowest category is observed at Lower Working-Class (DE) that has a mean value of 50.0
